~ freq_tutorial
Tut: You can use your [wave amp=5 freq=5][color=f06060]collar[/color][/wave] to vibe the frequency of this doors magnetic lock

do SignalBus.freq_tut_show_stick.emit( "show" )

Tut: Rotate the right analog stick {{ICON_RIGHT_STICK}} to change the frequnecy wave to match (vibe) with the lock's (yellow) frequency and HOLD it long enough

do SignalBus.freq_tut_show_stick.emit( "hide" )

#Tut: A lot of things in this world use a similar magnetic lock you can disrupt with your [color=f06060]collar[/color]. Many a lot harder than this little doorlock

do SignalBus.freq_tut_show_stick.emit( "auto" )
